<document xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xmlns:z="http://www.ebi.ac.uk/z" source="Whatizit"><text><SENT sid="0" pm="."><plain><z:hpo ids='HP_0000545'>Myopia</z:hpo> is the most common <z:e sem="disease" ids="C0034951" disease_type="Disease or Syndrome" abbrv="">refractive error</z:e> <z:hpo ids='HP_0000545'>Myopia</z:hpo> has been well established as a multifactorial disease with both genetic and environmental etiology </plain></SENT>
<SENT sid="1" pm="."><plain>A number of genetic loci have been linked with <z:hpo ids='HP_0000545'>myopia</z:hpo> </plain></SENT>
<SENT sid="2" pm="."><plain>We have described the prevalence and the symptoms of systemic disorders associated with <z:hpo ids='HP_0000545'>myopia</z:hpo>, including: Stickler <z:e sem="disease" ids="C0024796" disease_type="Disease or Syndrome" abbrv="MFS|MFS1">syndrome, Marfan</z:e> <z:e sem="disease" ids="C0013720" disease_type="Disease or Syndrome;Congenital Abnormality" abbrv="">syndrome, Ehlers-Danlos</z:e> syndrome, <z:e sem="disease" ids="C0265313" disease_type="Disease or Syndrome;Congenital Abnormality" abbrv="">Weill-Marchesani syndrome</z:e>, <z:hpo ids='HP_0002156'>homocystinuria</z:hpo>, <z:e sem="disease" ids="C0242292" disease_type="Disease or Syndrome" abbrv="POFD">McCune-Albright syndrome</z:e>, <z:e sem="disease" ids="C0265279" disease_type="Disease or Syndrome;Congenital Abnormality" abbrv="">Kniest syndrome</z:e>, <z:e sem="disease" ids="C0013080" disease_type="Disease or Syndrome;Congenital Abnormality" abbrv="">Down syndrome</z:e>, Prader-Willi syndrome, Noonan syndrome, <z:e sem="disease" ids="C0265223" disease_type="Disease or Syndrome" abbrv="">Cohen syndrome</z:e>, Rubinstein-<z:e sem="disease" ids="C0265251" disease_type="Disease or Syndrome;Congenital Abnormality" abbrv="">Taybi syndrome</z:e>, <z:e sem="disease" ids="C0270972" disease_type="Disease or Syndrome;Congenital Abnormality" abbrv="CDL|CDLS|BDLS|CDLS1">Cornelia de Lange syndrome</z:e> and <z:e sem="disease" ids="C0015923" disease_type="Disease or Syndrome" abbrv="FAE|ARBD">fetal alcohol syndrome</z:e> </plain></SENT>
</text></document>